---
title: "Software"
---

## ppseq

An R package of functions to design clinical trials with sequential Bayesian predictive probability monitoring for futility. Currently functionality is available for one-arm and two-arm clinical trials, and functionality for basket trials is under development. 

```{r out.width='300px', echo=FALSE}
knitr::include_graphics("images/ppseq.png")
```

Details at [http://www.emilyzabor.com/ppseq/](http://www.emilyzabor.com/ppseq/)


## riskclustr

An R  package of functions for the study of etiologic heterogeneity. 

Details at [https://www.emilyzabor.com/riskclustr/](https://www.emilyzabor.com/riskclustr/)


## condsurv

A package for conditional survival analysis. 

```{r out.width='300px', echo=FALSE}
knitr::include_graphics("images/condsurv.png")
```

Details at [https://www.emilyzabor.com/condsurv/](https://www.emilyzabor.com/condsurv/)